<strong>Cryosilk Robe - AC 11</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/chest.shtml">Chest</a><BR>
Weight: 1.0 - DEF, ERU, GNM, HIE, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/enchanter/armour/chest.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/chest.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/chest.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/chest.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) <BR>
(STA +13) (DEX +9) (INT +13) (Mana +35) </font>
<BR>
Submitted By: TregareUS<BR>

