<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Zellis</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-05 04:52:09</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well, I've done the Plane of Fear around a dozen times now and our server does it just about daily.  I have never seen one drop and I know for a fact there aren't any on our server (Brell Serilis).  I have heard from many people that it's been taken out of the game, but that may just be rumor.  Cryosilk armor IS dropped off the Spinechiller Spiders.  How do I know? I have a Cryosilk Amice and Choker.  Cryosilk itself is not that rare however the robe must be.  And last but not least Cryosilk armor is not Enchanter only, it is MAG,ENC,WIZ,NEC and it isn't the best drop for enchanters. The best robes for enchanters are 1: the Crimson Robe of Alendine (off of Cazic Thule) 2: the Insidious Robe (off of Female Revenants in the Plane of Hate).  However if any enchanter got this robe I'm sure they wouldn't complain.<BR>
<BR>
Zellis <Silent Redemption><BR>
Lvl 50 Magician </font></td></tr></table>
